      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the ideal balance between luxury and utility. Mechanically, this car is in excellent shape; the engine pulls strong without any hesitation, and the transmission delivers crisp, smooth shifts through every gear. I have strictly followed a preventative maintenance schedule, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of brake pads. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, maintaining a high-gloss finish. Upon close inspection, you will find minor signs of careful use, such as a few light stone chips on the hood and a small, superficial scratch near the fuel door, but no major dents or structural issues. Inside, the interior remains a highlight. The leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, the carpets have been protected by weather-mats since day one, and every piece of technology\u2014from the navigation system to the heated seats\u2014operates exactly as it should. The tires are premium-brand with approximately 75% tread life remaining. This is a turnkey car that requires nothing but a new driver.",
